cil.\nY como siempre, Metacam\u00ae40, nuestro nuevo Metacam\u00ae vacuno, ayuda a mejorar la productividad y act\u00faa m\u00e1s all\u00e1 de los resultados a corto plazo, aportando beneficios a largo plazo.", "language": null, "image": "https://i0.wp.com/www.produccionanimal.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/BOEHRINGER-metacam-DESTACADA.jpg?fit=4957%2C3966&ssl=1", "pagetype": "article", "links": ["#", "https://www.produccionanimal.com/ultimos-dias-para-participar-en-los-premios-bvdzero-espana-2023/", "https://www.produccionanimal.com/una-filosofia-en-la-medicacion-del-agua/", "https://www.produccionanimal.com/cargos-directivos-de-anembe/", "https://www.produccionanimal.com/noticias-blog/porcino/", "https://www.produccionanimal.com/porcino-capa-blanca/", "https://www.produccionanimal.com/porcino-iberico/", "https://www.produccionanimal.com/noticias-blog/bovino/", "https://www.produccionanimal.com/bovino-de-carne/", "https://www.produccionanimal.com/bovino-de-leche/", "https://www.produccionanimal.com/pequenos-rumiantes/", "https://www.produccionanimal.com/ovino/", "https://www.produccionanimal.com/caprino/", "https://www.produccionanimal.com/avicultura-3/", "https://www.produccionanimal.com/aviso-legal/", "https://www.produccionanimal.com/18873-2/", "https://somosrumis.es/", "https://www.produccionanimal.com/", "https://www.produccionanimal.com/noticias-blog/porcino/", "https://www.produccionanimal.com/porcino-capa-blanca/", "https://www.produccionanimal.com/porcino-iberico/", "https://www.produccionanimal.com/noticias-blog/bovino/", "https://www.produccionanimal.com/bovino-de-carne/", "https://www.produccionanimal.com/bovino-de-leche/", "https://www.produccionanimal.com/pequenos-rumiantes/", "https://www.produccionanimal.com/ovino/", "https://www.produccionanimal.com/caprino/", "https://www.produccionanimal.com/avicultura-3/", "https://www.produccionanimal.com/aviso-legal/", "https://www.produccionanimal.com/18873-2/", "https://www.produccionanimal.com/category/actua